ğŸ“Œ Overview

This project is a MERN stack application (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) configured to demonstrate:

Unit testing (React + Jest + Testing Library)

Integration testing (Node/Express + Supertest)

End-to-end testing (Cypress)

Debugging techniques (client + server)

CI/CD automation with GitHub Actions

Code coverage reporting (Jest)

The repository contains a full scaffolding for both client and server environments.

ğŸš€ Getting Started
